<div class="com-share" data-id="16348" data-title="《贝爷来中国做节目，是来当导游带明星团建的？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16348/medium/16348.jpg?1445330366" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16348.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
